<div class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero-text">
    <div class="about-kicker">Our story</div>
    <div class="about-title">About<br>Velnora Pets</div>
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <p class="about-p">We believe every pet deserves premium care. Velnora Pets was built to bring stylish, high-quality pet accessories to pet owners across the USA — all curated with love, all shipped fast.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-icon-box">
    <svg width="80" height="70" viewBox="0 0 40 36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="7" cy="11" r="4" fill="#c9a96e"/>
      <circle cx="15" cy="7" r="3.5" fill="#c9a96e"/>
      <circle cx="25" cy="7" r="3.5" fill="#c9a96e"/>
      <circle cx="33" cy="11" r="4" fill="#c9a96e"/>
      <ellipse cx="20" cy="27" rx="11" ry="9" fill="#c9a96e"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sec">
  <div class="sec-kicker">What we stand for</div>
  <div class="sec-title">Our values</div>
  <div class="sec-rule"></div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon"><i class="ti ti-heart" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
      <div class="val-title">Made with love</div>
      <div class="val-desc">Every product is hand-selected with your pet's wellbeing in mind. No compromises on quality or safety.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon"><i class="ti ti-shield-check" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
      <div class="val-title">Trusted suppliers</div>
      <div class="val-desc">We partner only with verified USA-based suppliers — fast shipping, reliable stock, and pet-safe materials.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon"><i class="ti ti-star" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
      <div class="val-title">Premium quality</div>
      <div class="val-desc">From bandanas to grooming kits — every item meets our quality standard before it reaches your door.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon"><i class="ti ti-truck" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
      <div class="val-title">Fast delivery</div>
      <div class="val-desc">All orders ship from US warehouses in 1–3 business days and arrive within 3–8 days nationwide.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="team-banner">
  <div class="team-text">
    <div class="team-title">Built for pet lovers</div>
    <div class="team-rule"></div>
    <p class="team-p">Velnora Pets was founded with one simple goal — make it easy for every pet owner to find beautiful, functional accessories without overpaying. We do the sourcing so you don't have to.</p>
    <div class="team-btns">
      <a href="/" class="btn-solid">Shop now</a>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn-out">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="team-stat-grid">
    <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">500+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Products</div></div>
    <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">3–8</div><div class="stat-lbl">Day ship</div></div>
    <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">4.8</div><div class="stat-lbl">Avg rating</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Page"
}
{% endschema %}
